INSTALL
  Download and install Hunspell lib at http://hunspell.sourceforge.net/
  Install RubyInline gem (sudo gem install RubyInline)
  In your source code:
    require "{PATH_TO}/hunspell"

USAGE
  dict = Hunspell.new("names.aff", "names.dic")

  dict.check("acetech") # => true
  dict.check("abcxyz")  # => false

	dict.suggest("azetach") # => "acetech"  

REFERENCES
  Hunspell programming interface: 
    http://sourceforge.net/docman/display_doc.php?docid=115683&group_id=143754

  Hunspell gem: 
    http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=4396
